                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020113-94-defend887 t18020113-94-punish506"></join>
               find sureties for his good behaviour for six months more
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>London Jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
